{"tid":2315772,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜隊友驚傳「曾接觸確診者」官方認TWICE全員檢測中","createTime":"2020-12-07T11:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T20:47:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"897ff6a1ea69392f8a88c5fdba11ee98c192fcb2","tid":2315772,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"南韓女團twice中的台灣成員周子瑜，靠著甜美仙氣的外表，去年還獲選美國電影網站TC Candler公布「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜奪得冠軍。不料近日卻傳出其中一位日籍成員SANA曾與確診武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）的女星請夏密集接觸過，官方也證實目前全員都在接受檢測中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922661-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922661-PH.jpg&h=10de4580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE日籍成員sana（左1）傳出與請夏接觸過。（圖／翻攝Mnet粉專）<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓媒體報導，TWICE日籍成員sana6日曾與女歌手請夏密切接觸過，請夏7日確診，也因此sana所屬的團體TWICE成為高風險群，經紀公司JYP也在稍早證實7日下午整團都接受檢測，也會根據檢測結果遵守政府規則。有鑒於TWICE6日晚間才剛參加完南韓大型典禮MAMA，是否會造成大規模染疫，也成為全球關注焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/02/29/2431300-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F02%2F29%2F2431300-PH.jpg&h=2a52ba17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲請夏證實確診。（圖／翻攝自請夏IG）"},{"pid":"788b2f9ea056cd88d0078d7fcda34989166c7178","tid":2315772,"uid":46933,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"全隊一齊被深喉檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29ed6836e5757fe226f5b7280713641e561f143","tid":2315772,"uid":74065,"like":28,"dislike":37,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"希望TWICE成隊死晒啦"},{"pid":"46168488b01ee3e9486eb613647d06f08a5c2092","tid":2315772,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e29ed6836e5757fe226f5b7280713641e561f143","tid":2315772,"uid":74065,"like":28,"dislike":37,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"希望TWICE成隊死晒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12